(1, '2026-02-25 03:09:08', '127.0.0.1', 'louise@indigotree.co.uk', '[Louise Towler Site] Some plugins were automatically updated', 'Howdy! Some plugins have automatically updated to their latest versions on your site at https://berkhamcouns.wpenginepowered.com. No further action is needed on your part.\n\n\nThese plugins are now up to date:\n- Perfmatters (from version 2.5.2 to 2.5.7) : https://perfmatters.io/downloads/perfmatters/?changelog=1\n- Accessibility Checker Pro (from version 1.18.0 to 1.20.0) : https://my.equalizedigital.com/downloads/accessibility-checker-pro/?changelog=1\n- Accessibility Checker: Audit History (from version 1.3.0 to 1.4.0) : https://my.equalizedigital.com/downloads/accessibility-checker-audit-history/?changelog=1\n- Schema Pro (from version 2.10.4 to 2.10.7) : https://wpschemapro.com/pricing/\n- Gravity Forms (from version 2.9.21 to 2.9.28) : https://gravityforms.com\n\n\nIf you experience any issues or need support, the volunteers in the WordPress.org support forums may be able to help.\nhttps://wordpress.org/support/forums/\n\nThe WordPress Team', 'Content-Type: text/html', '', NULL, '1.16.0') ;
